:"2019-08-05T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"你咪唔好信 呢個係我今日係沙田見到嘅實際情況"},{"pid":"4816035d3e8a69802f0fae37d1b20e6fb954818c","tid":1417994,"uid":206246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"340237b7db7fa9850ab87771b69d215b83d6ecaf","tid":1417994,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"全港流浪狗位置實時地圖上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cAzgTon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAzgTon.png&h=5d46c5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，本人寫左個好似google doc咁既地圖<br />\n<br />\n睇緊live既即刻入黎幫手報料!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=90ea489c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n見到多狗, 即刻mark番落地圖<br />\n視乎數量就算已經報左都可以報多一次<br />\n幫手傳出去 等義士唔好再食布袋戰術<br />\nBe Water!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=90ea489c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a>"},{"pid":"11b559b830160ea83eabbdb39061da4032db5a6b","tid":1417994,"uid":241397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"(急)(大家入黎討論)發夢頭先黃大仙 見證班狗新招 夜戰要好小心<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxfymS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxfymS</a> <br />\n  <br />\n入夜後，啲狗係近新蒲崗橋底極速築好防線，因為入夜好難睇 <br />\n推之前已經有幾下熄街燈 <br />\n當佢推到係宿舍個街口，突然開頭燈，之後街燈熄左，班狗即刻狗衝 <br />\n我係上面係完全睇唔到情況係點 <br />\n1. 太黑 <br />\n2. 有大光燈照住 <br />\n係好撚恐怖，啲狗係極速推到去龍翔道，完全睇唔到前線情況，唔知有冇義士被咬同人踩人出現，有冇前線手足報情況？ <br />\n<br />\n大家入黎討論<br />\n點撚樣算！！！！！"},{"pid":"cadb51f431cdcca534be8fb94b3f6cbcf926de40","tid":1417994,"uid":120555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"e874b21e0dab027c9b52227a97524fcd11bbeb32","tid":1417994,"uid":206246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eedc5e9787c90e92ed94bbcf235493f9285d305b","tid":1417994,"uid":206246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40fb72ba77b2ad5f54d51bdf94b92f62d7889972","tid":1417994,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"前線唔係大台<br />\n<br />\n依場運動特色係無大台"},{"pid":"9853e891619186d3662fd39345c261a67160d934","tid":1417994,"uid":239313,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"放火係鬼"},{"pid":"b0ad612cb49748507f1e4ce713555fb848dd56ac","tid":1417994,"uid":187950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1ce4592734edb55337980385b07d2786f424719","tid":1417994,"uid":206246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"如題 就如小弟今日係沙田嘅夢境所見 有唔少手足好燥 一心只係想打狗 我明白狗真係好撚on9 但其實唔應該為打而打 應該要定目標去做 唔應該只為打狗 唔係話打狗唔應該 <br />\n但我覺得應該要理性 唔好成為自己所憎恨嘅人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得打狗就唔洗客氣 你為政權服務與民為敵 所以狗係目標之一"},{"pid":"c0884d9e5d5ca39e4105a2ee192e18daeabfebcd","tid":1417994,"uid":124811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n都係果句 對準政權"},{"pid":"70939850dca4c5138ae5a47eb9fb08a32eb27037","tid":1417994,"uid":281143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"我都係咁講，我個post仲有好多人講唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /